karate
Copy
Edit
Feature: Get owner

Scenario: Get existing owner
  Given url 'http://localhost:8080'
  And path '/owners/1'
  When method GET
  Then status 200
  And match response ==
    """
    {
      "ownerId": "1",
      "licenseNumber": "XYZ123",
      "postalCode": "12345",
      "name": "John Doe"
    }
    """
